the Nazis finding people.

1590
02:04:48,880 --> 02:04:52,008
And, yes, some of them
were Jews. But Jew Hunter?

1591
02:04:53,343 --> 02:04:55,219
J ust a name that stuck.

1592
02:04:55,678 --> 02:04:58,473
Well, you do have to
admit, it is catchy.

1593
02:04:59,933 --> 02:05:03,102
Do you control the nicknames
your enemies bestow on you?

1594
02:05:03,186 --> 02:05:05,688
Aldo the Apache
and the Little Man?

1595
02:05:06,773 --> 02:05:08,900
What do you mean
the Little Man?

1596
02:05:08,983 --> 02:05:10,777
Germans' nickname for you.

1597
02:05:10,860 --> 02:05:13,905
The Germans' nickname for me
is the Little Man?

1598
02:05:14,280 --> 02:05:18,826
And as if to make my point, I'm a little
surprised how tall you were in real life.

1599
02:05:18,910 --> 02:05:21,329
I mean, you're a little fellow,
but not circus-midget little,

1600
02:05:21,412 --> 02:05:23,206
as your reputation
would suggest.

1601
02:05:23,289 --> 02:05:24,832
Where's my men?

1602
02:05:25,375 --> 02:05:27,710
Where's
Bridget von Hammersmark?

1603
02:05:30,588 --> 02:05:33,758
Well, let's just say,
she got what she deserved.

1604
02:05:36,261 --> 02:05:38,763
And when you purchase friends
like Bridget von Hammersmark,

1605
02:05:38,846 --> 02:05:40,848
you get what you pay for.

1606
02:05:42,267 --> 02:05:47,272
Now as far as your paesanos,
Sergeant Donowitz and Private Omar...

1607
02:05:47,355 --> 02:05:49,274
How you know our names?

1608
02:05:49,857 --> 02:05:51,442
Lieutenant Aldo,

1609
02:05:53,319 --> 02:05:54,737
if you don't think
I wouldn't interrogate

1610
02:05:54,821 --> 02:05:58,199
every single one of your
swastika-marked survivors,

1611
