You go now, and we'll see you after the show.

1727
02:17:44,647 --> 02:17:45,688
Who is it?

1728
02:17:46,023 --> 02:17:47,065
Fredrick!

1729
02:17:48,526 --> 02:17:49,567
Shit.

1730
02:17:54,156 --> 02:17:56,366
